Base URL: http://localhost:3001/api

Auth
POST /auth/register - Create user {email, password, skills[]}
POST /auth/login - {email, password} → JWT token
GET /auth/profile - Get user profile (JWT req'd)

Creators
GET /creators - List creators, filter by skills
GET /creators/:id - Creator details/portfolio
PUT /creators/:id - Update profile

Projects
POST /projects - Create collab project {title, description, skillsNeeded[]}
GET /projects - Browse open projects
POST /projects/:id/apply - Apply to project (JWT)
GET /projects/:id/collaborators - Team members

Feedback
POST /feedback/:projectId - Submit review {rating, comment}

Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
